"2 pounds fingerling potatoes","3  (4-inch) fresh rosemary sprigs","2  garlic cloves","2  bay leaves","1/4 cup olive oil","2 teaspoons kosher salt","1  (2-oz.) salami piece, cut into thin strips","2 tablespoons chopped shallot (1/2 large shallot)","3 tablespoons sherry or red wine vinegar","1 tablespoon Dijon mustard","2 teaspoons sorghum syrup or honey","1/4 teaspoon dried crushed red pepper","1/3 cup olive oil","2 cups loosely packed baby arugula","1 tablespoon chopped fresh tarragon or basil"